description:
Information W@r: Tyrants @ WEF Hate Liberty. World Economic Forum: Rebuilding Trust In 2024 vs Anti-System Movement. Questions & Answers: Study The Final Two Seals

1. Under the 6th seal a great earthquake occurs, Revelation 6:12. What was the date?
A. November 13, 1833
B. March 21, 1843
C. November 1, 1755
D. October 22, 1844

2.  Under the 6th seal, the sun became black & the moon became red, Revelation 6:12.  What was the date?
A. October 22, 1844
B. May 19, 1780
C. August 11, 1840
D. November 1, 1780

3. Under the 6th seal, stars fell to the earth, Revelation 6:13. What was the date?
A. March 21, 1843
B. May 19, 1780
C. August 11, 1840
D. November 13, 1833

Note: Under the 6th seal, the second coming of Jesus was delayed.  Read Revelation 6:14-17 and Revelation 7:1-3.

4. Under the 6th seal, the sealing of Gods people occurs, Revelation 7:1-3. What three parts comprise a Biblical seal?
A. Name, title, territory
B. Name, pedigree, occupation
C. Past, present future
D. 1st, 2nd, 3rd Angels Messages

5.  Gods seal is found in His law, which of the 10 Commandments contain Gods seal?
A. 7th
B. 4th
C. 1st
D. 6th

6. In addition to keeping the 7th-day Sabbath, people who are sealed dont do which of the following?
A. Evangelize
B. Fast and Pray
C. Depart from sin
D. Reverse to sin

7. Luke 21:25, 26 are additional signs under the 6th seal. Based on the time period of events in verse 25, which did not fulfill distress of nations?
A. Tribulation in Dark Ages
B. The Great Depression
C. WWI
D. WWII

Note: Luke 21:25, 26 mentions fear among nations. The word fear means terror, terrorism and alarm of war. See Strongs Exhaustive Concordance of the Bible, Greek Lexicon number 5401 

8. Which event launched the global war on terrorism in America?
A. Pearl Harbor Attack
B. The Gulf War/Desert Storm
C. September 11 Attacks
D. The Holocaust 

9. Luke 21:31, 32 states that this generation shall not pass How many years comprise a Biblical generation?
A. 30 years
B. 40 years
C. 120 years
D. 160 years

10. Under the 7th seal there was silence in heaven, according to Revelation 8:1.  What event caused this silence?
A. Mourning Christs Death on the cross
B. The falling of the 7 last plagues
C. Mourning Satans & 1/3 of the angels being cast out of heaven
D. The Second Coming of Jesus

11. Under the 7th seal there was silence in heaven about the space of half an hour, Revelation 8:1. Half an hour represents how many literal days, according to prophetic interpretation?
A. 1 day
B. 3 days
C. 7 days
D. 10 days
